The only option I can think of in span conversion are hacks:
* for address keyword in "sa" "ca" "ma"
  * leniently treat any binary annotation with address keyword as truthy (ex ignore the value which would let `"1"` be same as `true`. The value is actually unimportant.
  * drop any binary annotation which has address keyword and a value besides true.

